## Usage Notes

### For App Integration
```javascript
// Example usage
const satpinData = require('./satpin-words.json');

// Get words by pattern
const cvcWords = satpinData.words.CVC;

// Get teaching sequence
const week1Words = satpinData.teaching_sequence.week_1.words;

// Filter high-frequency for beginners
const starterWords = satpinData.high_frequency_subset;
```

### For Flashcard Generation
- Use `words` object to filter by pattern type
- Apply `teaching_sequence` for structured progression
- Include `assessment_words.nonsense` for testing
- Reference `cantonese_difficulty` for differentiation

